Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For this final video in the series, we're gonna cover some placement of objects,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For this final video in the series, we're gonna cover some placement of objects,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we're also going to cover maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,placing an AI character inside the level,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and also dragging out a navmesh to be able to give it interaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So to begin, what we can do is we can focus on the idea of placing a hut,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because this was what, I guess if I lived on an island, I figured that I would be building a hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So we go to the create objects tab and let's go to architecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,buildings and we can go to the forest_cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's double click this and bring this out into our level.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I don't know exactly which side the door is on,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,obviously this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and we can pull this back into
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the actual woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:01:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this would be one of those cases where you need to cull wherever the vegetation is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's go ahead and close material editor, level settings,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,when go back to the vegetation editor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and let's find the actual bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe we just get rid it of bush, so it's out of the way quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we have a nice little cabin,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think that we would like a nice little dock,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,not exactly sure where it is, inside of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so maybe we can type it in, plus we can search.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We open the assets/objects/props/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,maritime/wooden_dock,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's cool, we have a nice little dock,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and we can click and add,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's click the 2 key, we can add that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's keep in mind one other thing is we can actually duplicate this dock,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we duplicate it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,can open up this, let's change the vegetation editor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,just go ahead and close all these.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we can change the dock inside of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe it's something else that we would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go ahead and change one more, you can quickly test things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that otherwise you may not have an idea of what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I like this right here, this dock and maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we can use this one as the end piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This other one looks kind of big, so
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to start out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that this will probably be the end, just because
