Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we said that we wanted to add an AI character to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so if I go back to my entities
